title: Sample Note
text:
Welcome to your brand new Note Taker!
To add a note click the + in the upper right.
Once you've filled the title and text fields, click the Save button to store your note for later.
You can delete a note by clicking its trash can button. Be careful: once you delete a note it's gone forever!
